	Please write the instructions to run your code here

******************************************************************************************************
	- Download the datset form the following link (~12GB): https://uni-bonn.sciebo.de/s/yBdM6exK2zvCKr3 

	- If you are using the machines from our lab, plaese do not place the dataset in the home directory. Instead, create a folder with your name under /media/data

	- The groundTruth directory contains the frame-wise labels for the videos (one file per video).

	- The features directory contains the frame-wise features for the videos (one file per video, and each file is a numpy array with dimention 2048xT).

	- In the following is a breif description of the files included in the data folder

		mapping.txt: List of the action classes and the corresponding id
	
		train.bundle: List of the training videos (Make sure to use the suitable path and extension to read the features or action labels)

		test.bundle: List of the testing videos (Make sure to use the suitable path and extension to read the features or action labels)
